p.d: Do not miss the first part of Barcelona Heat, a film by Bobby Peru, where a newly married couple decide to go to Barcelona for their honeymoon. The mysterious sudden disappearance of the bride quickly turns their dream vacation into a desperate search full of sex and intrigue. Enjoy this movie starring Europe's finest: Erica Fontes, Alexis Crystal, Violette Pink, Tiffany Doll, Noemilk, Alicia Poz, Julie Hunter and Lullu Gun. We're already looking forward to the second part!
